</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>In the <computeroutput>header.html</computeroutput> template, include <computeroutput>doxygen-awesome-paragraph-link.js</computeroutput> at the end of the <computeroutput>&lt;head&gt;</computeroutput> and then initialize it: ```html &lt;html&gt; &lt;head&gt;</para>
